\nc<Senpai>Are you finished? Then let's try doing some promotional work
today as part of your training.
\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>Yes! What kind of promotion should I do?

\nc<Senpai>First, I've prepared a uniform for you, so go ahead and
change into it.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>(I thought I'd be working in a suit...)\bustMsgExp[1, 3]A
uniform, you say? Understood.
\bustMsgExp[1, 4]\nc<Saki>Hehehe, I wonder what kind of uniform it is...

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>(Eh... wait, is this... is this right? Such an outrageous
uniform?)

\nc<Saki>(Everyone's acting so calm!?\bustMsgExp[1, 2]I would have
preferred something like what Senpai is wearing...)

\bustMoveTo[2, -100, 720, 30]\nc<Senpai>It suits you well. From now on, you'll basically be wearing
that uniform.
\nc<Senpai>Now, let's head to the city. Here, take this.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(Promotion means this? This is totally like a flyer for an
escort service...)
\nc<Senpai>Oh, you said you were originally human, right?

\bustMsgExp[2, 2]\nc<Senpai>The succubus industry involves taking life force from
customers.

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Yes. You get aroused when you do naughty things, right? We
collect that arousal.
\nc<Senpai>Don't worry so much. You'll get used to it quickly.

\nc<Senpai>After all, succubi can't live without life force. Saki, you
might not understand since you've just become a succubus...
\nc<Saki>(The rumors were true... a race of natural-born bitches...)
\nc<Saki>(But... but...! I have nowhere else to go...)
